[{"index":1,"title":"牵念","content":"记得，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>那个多风的秋天，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>一丛野菊，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>默默，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>开在路边。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>我住了脚步，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>不由看了几眼，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>瑟瑟的风，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>立时缠缠绵绵。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>日子，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>匆匆忙忙，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>平平淡淡，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>那次秋风里的记忆，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>却在我生命里，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>渐渐蔓延。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>又是秋天，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>荷塘深处，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>飘过浅红的罗衫。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>几尾鱼儿戏水，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>莲叶田田。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>兰舟桂棹，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>划破水底的天，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>鸥鹭惊飞，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>惹起你动人的笑靥。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>时隔多年，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>我的肩头，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>还留有那一刻的温暖。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>闭上眼睛，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>你就在目前，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>而相逢，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>却如此艰难。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>你的微笑，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>已存了多年，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>那个旧梦，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>老也做不完。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>谁知今生，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>还能不能再见，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>枫叶飘忽，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>落满秋山。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>江飘日月，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>岁岁年年，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>往事，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>都幻了缕缕风烟。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>没有你的日子，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>牵念，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>丝丝缕缕，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>连起——&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>一江秋水，&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>山外青山。&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;\r<br>\u0018","author":"铃铛纯纯","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.c0b7e913.B14__KIANcUED4aHmFxI9A&fr=pb","date":"2007-06-08 13:22","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：牵念","content":"很不错的，你写的�","author":"夜迷茫","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.9dd7b6d1.MIb-DJWNvc5dEX4KU_s5FA?t=1472998162&fr=pb","date":"2007-06-08 13:24","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：牵念","content":"转...","author":"铃铛纯纯","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.c0b7